keyFacts: An unnamed individual feels that GM (likely Ghislaine Maxwell) is using media to intimidate her and other victims.
The note was created by Sunny Drescher, a contractor with USANYS, on November 23, 2021, regarding a call from November 22, 2021.
The document is subject to a protective order covering specific paragraphs (7, 8, 9, 10, 15, and 17).
